
---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **HTML5**, **CSS3**, **Vanilla JavaScript**
- **GitHub** for source control
- **Render.com** for deployment

---

## 🧩 Features

- ✅ Multi-page layout per sector
- ✅ Mobile-responsive design
- ✅ Structured nav bar and footer
- ✅ Ready for integration with:
  - CRM (Airtable or Notion API)
  - Email Marketing (Mailchimp)
  - Payments (Stripe)
  - Analytics (Google Tag Manager + GA4)

---

## ⚙️ How to Run Locally

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/nhalege-website.git
cd nhalege-website

# Open in browser
# You can right-click `index.html` and open in browser,
# or use a local server like Live Server in VS Code
